{"tid":1595296,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［屌你咩］中大：校園多處被密集噴漆塗污　保留紀律處分權利","createTime":"2019-09-26T03:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T04:12:02.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e903129463a0d1f699c71f3a6ab2c17ce24f19b6","tid":1595296,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"中文大學表示，校園近日有多處地方及建築物被肆意塗污，昨晚深夜至今日凌晨，校園本部多處地點更被不同人士密集式噴漆塗污，並以牆紙粉、膠漿張貼單張於地面，發言人形容，校園遭受大面積損污，面目全非，對此深表遺憾及痛心，強調對這類行為，大學會保留紀律處分的權利，如果涉及刑事毀壞，大學會嚴肅處理。<br />\n<br />\n中大在聲明表示，大學一直尊重各成員的言論自由，設有指定地方讓大家發表意見。但近日部分人士為表達個人意見，肆意於各處大範圍以噴漆塗污及張貼單張，破壞校園，妄顧其他校園使用者的權利及感受，有關行為不能以言論自由作為辯解。<span style=\"color: red;\">前線清潔員工要不斷清洗，疲於善後。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482654-20190926.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482654-20190926.htm&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRt9AtAt3lYzSqFOpIRNeugk%3D&h=03cf0498\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482654-20190926.htm&h=da18ac24\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482654-20190926.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好撚洗住咪得囉屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5edba56792fe33d646667c9d9ef91f0a05d2f69e","tid":1595296,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:40:13.000Z","msg":"去仆街啦條撚樣校長"},{"pid":"5a1a8c20d809315e4498ccfdb2878f181ba64c3e","tid":1595296,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:05:50.000Z","msg":"搵日組隊返去一齊黐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c46870c855d341e041b37daaed653d270f4bc6c","tid":1595296,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:12:02.000Z","msg":"共大"}]}